@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = 请先填入 Bearer token

### 1. 查询尿酸记录
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/uric-acid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 查询体重记录
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/weight
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 查询血压记录
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/blood-pressure
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 查询补水记录
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/hydration
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 查询发作记录
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/flares
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 查询统一记录中心
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/center
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 按类型筛选统一记录中心
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/center?types=WEIGHT&types=BLOOD_PRESSURE&types=URIC_ACID&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 只看补水与发作
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/center?types=HYDRATION&types=FLARE&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 非法类型示例
GET {{host}}/api/v1/records/center?types=MEAL&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
